background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:none;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;background-image:none;height:auto;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-right-width:3px;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Plate.js</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是一个为 React 开发者设计的富文本编辑器框架，构建于 Slate.js 之上，目标是</span><strong style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;padding-left:0px;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:none;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;background-image:none;height:auto;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-right-width:3px;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简化复杂编辑器的开发流程</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。它基于</span><strong style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;padding-left:0px;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-positio